Cyberpunk style: A massive holographic code scanner floating above a futuristic cityscape at night, projecting streams of glowing cyan and magenta data cascading through the air like digital waterfalls. In the foreground, intricate crystalline structures representing code blocks are being analyzed by sweeping laser beams that reveal hidden flaws as pulsing red nodes within the otherwise electric blue matrix. The scene features towering neon-lit server towers in the background, their surfaces covered in circuit-board patterns. Flying drones circle the central scanning apparatus, which resembles a giant eye made of interlocking geometric shapes. Rain falls through the holographic projections, creating prismatic light refractions. The atmosphere is moody with deep purple shadows and brilliant technological highlights, suggesting automated vigilance over vast digital architecture.
